I'm done for the night.

116
00:07:28,700 --> 00:07:30,220
Good.

117
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:32,420
- Champagne, huh?
- Yes.

118
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:34,860
- Celebrating?
- Do you want some?

119
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:38,260
- Sure.
- I'm done. You can take the rest with you.

120
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:40,620
Oh. Um...

121
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:42,620
- No, thanks.
- Take it. I'm done.

122
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:45,420
No. I'm driving. Um...

123
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:48,660
- I'll let myself out.
- Good.

124
00:07:48,740 --> 00:07:51,820
- When should I come back?
- Come back?

125
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:55,260
Yeah. I'm no way near finished.
Maybe tomorrow?

126
00:07:55,340 --> 00:07:57,860
We have a funeral tomorrow.

127
00:07:57,900 --> 00:08:02,500
You're right. I'm sorry.
I was going to attend, if that's all right.

128
00:08:02,540 --> 00:08:03,900
Sure.

129
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:06,020
What about Sunday?
Will you be around?

130
