- There's nothing up there.
- There are 103 notebooks.

134
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:19,860
He was a graphomaniac, Harold.
Do you know what that is?

135
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:21,740
He wrote compulsively.
Call me Hal.

136
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:25,300
