They don't play anything for three minutes.

147
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:57,860
Imaginary number?

148
00:08:57,900 --> 00:09:00,580
It's a math joke.
You see why they're way down the bill.

149
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:03,540
That's a long drive
to see some nerds in a band.

150
00:09:03,620 --> 00:09:07,220
I hate when people say that.
It's not really that long of a drive.

151
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:09,700
- So they are nerds.
- Oh, they're raging geeks.

152
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:12,020
But they're geeks
who can dress themselves

153
00:09:12,100 --> 00:09:14,260
and hold down a job at a major university.

154
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:17,700
Some of them have switched
from glasses to contacts.

155
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:21,980
They play sports. They play in a band.
